            <h4 class="blog-post-title mt-5">A low-code development platform: what is it?</h4>
            <p class="blog-post-meta text-justify">A low-code development platform is a software tool that allows users to create web applications with minimal coding knowledge. These tools streamline the development process and let developers concentrate on designing business logic and user interfaces rather than writing code using visual modeling tools and pre-built components. Businesses can use a low-code development platform to create web apps more quickly, affordably, and with less effort. </p>
            
            <h4 class="blog-post-title mt-5">The advantages of platforms for low-code development</h4>
            <ul class="bullet-point text-justify">
