            <li><strong class="font-weight-bold">Decreased expenses: </strong>By removing the requirement for in-depth coding expertise and cutting down on the development resources needed, low-code development platforms considerably lower development costs. Businesses may create web applications with fewer resources and at a lower price than with conventional development techniques by utilizing pre-built components and visual modeling tools.</li>
