            <li><strong class="font-weight-bold">Ease of collaboration:</strong> Low-code development platforms improve collaboration between developers and business users. Thanks to visual modeling tools and pre-built components, business users may offer input and modify apps without considerable coding skills. Through greater cooperation, firms may create apps that better serve the requirements of their customers and produce better financial results.</li>
            <li><strong class="font-weight-bold">Scalability and versatility:</strong> Low-code development platforms enable scalability and flexibility that may be lacking in typical development practices. Developers can easily update and alter apps using pre-built modules and graphical modeling techniques when business requirements change. Businesses can remain adaptable and react to shifting market conditions more swiftly with the support of the flexibility and scalability of low-code development methods.</li>
            </ul>

